
.container
  .page-header
    %h1 Import Orgs

  .well
    Must be a csv, xls, xlsx file with the following headers: "Agency Name", "Address 1", "Main Phone", "Address 1: City", "Primary Contact", "Email (Primary Contact) (Contact)", "Website", "Organization Type", "Agency Abbreviation". Orgs will be synced against "Agency Abbreviation"


  = form_tag admin_org_imports_path, multipart: true do
    = file_field_tag "org_import[file]"
    = submit_tag "Import", class: 'btn btn-default'